{
  "texts": [
    "You do not have much time to make up your mind and browse the internet looking for information.",
    "You run into predictions from an artificially intelligent poll, which are granular enough to reveal the political propensities of your neighbourhood.",
    "These predictions suggest widespread support for the far right.",
    "You could react in many ways.",
    "You could stick to your guns, choosing to continue cheering for the underdog."
  ]
}